      "text": "We play something, we play a game. A [[Game]]: that is obviously a different kind of [[Reality]] than the \"normal\" one, and playing a different activity than the normal one. What is different? This is the question [[Heinrich Popitz]] wants to clarify: What is this strange other reality that we create through play?"
    },
